snippet.title: W.A.N.D. Project | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
W.A.N.D. Project is OUT NOW and Tokyo needs YOU to defend the city!

The alien invasion has begun, and Tokyo is counting on YOU to step up as its defender. Wield the power of the Wands, craft endless spell combinations, and face the unknown.

The fate of the city – and maybe even the entire world – is in your hands.

Get the game here: 
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2581750/WAND_Project/
Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/us/store/products/w-a-n-d-project-switch

#WANDProject #roguelike #bullethell #spellcrafting #animegame #indiegame
